Once upon a time Sheet Music Boss uploaded piano tutorials for various Windows XP sounds. They sat around on the channel for a long time, merely a curiosity for people to stumble upon throughout YouTube. Finally the reason for these piano tutorials is revealed: a fantastic piano piece that uses the Windows XP sounds throughout as motifs! We hope you like this fantastic and fun piece: make sure to comment with your favourite part!
#WINDOWSXPSONATA #PianoTutorial #SheetMusicBoss
